data.description: Rare find! 5 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2 car garage with over 2,700 square feet plus in addition to all the bedrooms there is an additional living area on the 2nd floor that can be used as a playroom or home theater.**See 3d interactive virtual tour**  If that were not enough, there is a huge office with a built in desk and ample storage on the right as you enter the residence. This home does not lack storage. Additional storage under stairs and in attic.  Newly installed luxury vinyl plank flooring on first floor living area and kitchen. The kitchen is perfect for cooking or entertaining a large crowd with a walk-in pantry and lots of granite counter space.  Master suite is located on the first floor and the 4 additional bedrooms are upstairs. All bedrooms have walk-in closets.  Home has a huge fenced backyard with a first pit. The garage has a work bench with  extra built in cabinets and epoxy flooring.  This property is very centrally located with the Naval Air Station 20 minutes away, Downtown Pensacola 15 min and Pensacola Beach 25 min.  All measurements have been taken from taxdocuments, surveys, and MLS and are believed to be accurate, but buyers should verify all features, dimensions, measurements,that may be important to them. Ask your realtor about possibility of very low interest VA assumable mortgage.
